rces; night exterior uses porch lantern practical + moon rim; rain scene uses streetlight pools and reflective wet road as bounce; clinics use overhead fluorescent panels with minimal shadow.\n- **Mood:** fast-paced soap-opera beats with hard emotional turns; escalating stakes into a “dangerous procedure” cliffhanger.	provider	original	2026-04-23 16:07:03.728511+00
