2	1	2	scene	Banana woman realizes her face is ruined and panics at a dirty bathroom mirror	Vertical 9:16. High-end 3D animated cinematic style. In a grimy, dim bathroom, the **Banana Woman (anthropomorphic banana, species: Musaceae)** stands close to a stained mirror over a sink. FULL ANCHOR: tall and slim with athletic build, ripe-yellow peel skin, banana-shaped head with peeled-back top forming thick curved peel “hair” draped backward; no visible accessories; distinguishing marks: none visible. Clothing: fitted sleeveless black ribbed mini dress. She raises both hands near her face in shock, fingers spread, shoulders hunched; expression implied distressed as she stares at her reflection. Mirror shows the same Banana Woman reflection, emphasizing anxiety. Environment: cracked/dirty wall tiles, an old mirror with grime and water spots, a small shelf or sink edge with toiletry bottles (one tall white bottle, one shorter bottle), and a rectangular soap bar on the counter. Lighting: harsh, cool-white bathroom bulb above mirror creating unflattering highlights and deep shadows under the “peel hair.” Color palette: dirty gray, muted beige, yellow, black. Camera: medium close-up from behind-left of the Banana Woman, capturing reflection and hands. Mood: panic, self-disgust.	Duration ~6s. Camera locked off; slight handheld micro-jitter for anxiety. The Banana Woman (anthropomorphic banana, species: Musaceae) leans closer to the mirror, head tilting left then right as if checking damage. Her hands rise from chest level to cheek level, trembling; fingers splay, then clutch slightly. She recoils half a step, breathing fast.\n\nSPEAKER BLOCKING:\n- Banana Woman: "ولّيتي مقززة دابا… ما نقدرش نشوف فيك… عمرَك ترجعي لهاذ الدار." ⚠️ ONLY Banana Woman speaks these lines—Banana Woman mouth moves in the reflection; all other mouths (none present) remain closed.\n\nTransition: smash cut to a luxury wood-paneled office with an eggplant boss looming. Emotional arc: from shock to being verbally destroyed.	Banana Woman: "ولّيتي مقززة دابا… ما نقدرش نشوف فيك… عمرَك ترجعي لهاذ الدار."	Ambience: dripping faucet, faint bathroom fan rattle. Music: tense strings swell at ~80 BPM, rising. SFX: mirror cabinet creak; subtle breath/hand rustle on fabric. Mix: dialogue clear; music swells at end to lead into hard cut.	الموزة كتشوف وجهها فمراية حمّام موسّخ وكتصدم حيث ولات مشوّهة، وكتغرق فالهلع وكتحقر راسها.	data:image/jpeg;base64,
3	1	3	scene	Eggplant husband/boss screams at the banana woman and orders her out of the house	Vertical 9:16. High-end 3D animated cinematic style in an opulent study. A **Eggplant Man (anthropomorphic eggplant, species: Solanum melongena)** stands behind a large dark-wood desk, leaning forward aggressively and pointing toward frame left. FULL ANCHOR: very tall and muscular/stocky upper body, deep-purple glossy eggplant skin, large eggplant-shaped head with a green calyx cap on top like hair; thick furrowed brow ridges; large round eyes (color not clearly readable), heavy-lidded angry glare; broad nose ridge; wide mouth with clenched teeth; no facial hair; distinguishing marks: none visible. Clothing: charcoal-gray three-piece suit (jacket, vest), white dress shirt, medium-gray tie; no accessories. Seated in a green velvet armchair at desk left is the **Banana Woman (anthropomorphic banana, species: Musaceae)** FULL ANCHOR: tall slim athletic, ripe-yellow peel skin, banana head with peeled-back peel “hair” draped backward; fitted sleeveless black ribbed mini dress; no accessories; posture small and intimidated, hands near lap, head tilted down. Environment: wood-paneled library walls, tall bookshelves packed with books, ornate chandelier overhead, a fireplace glow off-frame, large window showing sunset sky, framed oil painting on wall, globe and laptop on desk, a short tumbler glass with amber liquid on desk right, stacks of cash near the laptop. A small dog lies on a rug near the chair (partially visible). Camera: medium-wide, eye-level. Lighting: warm tungsten from chandelier and lamps, strong highlights on wood and glass. Palette: walnut-brown, gold, emerald-green, deep purple. Mood: domineering, humiliating confrontation.	Duration ~10s. Start with a medium-wide static shot. The Eggplant Man (anthropomorphic eggplant, species: Solanum melongena) slams a fist onto the desk (small desk vibration), then jabs a finger toward the Banana Woman (anthropomorphic banana, species: Musaceae). He leans closer, shoulders squared, face contorting from disgust to rage. The Banana Woman shrinks into the green chair, shoulders collapsing, hands clutching at her dress hem; she looks up pleadingly.\n\nSPEAKER BLOCKING:\n- Banana Woman: "علاش؟ عافاك ما تخليشني!" ⚠️ ONLY Banana Woman speaks—Eggplant Man mouth fully closed during her plea, only glares.\n- Eggplant Man: "سكتي إلا كنتي كتهضري معايا!" ⚠️ ONLY Eggplant Man speaks—Banana Woman mouth fully closed; she flinches and averts gaze.\n\nTransition: cut to a luxury fashion store where the strawberry woman flirts with the eggplant man. Emotional arc: rejection and domination.	Banana Woman: "علاش؟ عافاك ما تخليشني!"\nEggplant Man: "سكتي إلا كنتي كتهضري معايا!"	Ambience: quiet mansion room tone, faint fireplace crackle. Music: dramatic orchestral sting with low brass at ~90 BPM. SFX: desk thump impact, finger jab whoosh, chair upholstery creak, glass clink on desk. Mix: dialogue loud and dry; music punctuates the fist slam then ducks under speech.	راجلها/الباطرون الباذنجان كيغوت عليها وكيأمرها تخرج، وهي كتترجاه وهو كيسكتها بعنف.	data:image/jpeg;base64,
4	1	4	scene	Strawberry woman flirts with Mr. Squashalino in a Balenciaga store; he accepts	Vertical 9:16. High-end 3D animated cinematic style in a modern luxury fashion boutique. Center frame: the **Eggplant Man (anthropomorphic eggplant, species: Solanum melongena)** FULL ANCHOR: very tall and muscular/stocky, deep-purple glossy eggplant skin, eggplant head with green calyx cap on top; heavy angry brow ridges and large round eyes; broad nose ridge; wide mouth now neutral-to-pleased; no facial hair; no visible marks. Clothing: charcoal-gray three-piece suit, white dress shirt, medium-gray tie; no accessories. Frame right: the **Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman (anthropomorphic strawberry, species: Fragaria)** stands close, lightly holding his forearm as she compliments him. FULL ANCHOR: average height compared to him (shorter by a head), slim build, glossy red strawberry skin with seed speckles, green leaf crown topped with small white flowers, small green stem; eyes and mouth not clearly readable in the sample but expression implies flirtatious; clothing: white lab coat worn open over a light top; bright-blue nitrile gloves; no jewelry visible. Environment: industrial concrete walls and ceiling with linear fluorescent lights, clothing racks with neutral coats, large “BALENCIAGA” signage on wall and on display blocks, shoppers blurred in background. Camera: medium shot, eye-level. Lighting: cool, even fluorescent. Palette: concrete gray, black, white, deep purple, red. Mood: transactional flirting, upscale coldness.	Duration ~8s. Camera slow lateral slide left-to-right as the Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman (anthropomorphic strawberry, species: Fragaria) steps into the Eggplant Man’s personal space and taps his suited arm twice with her blue-gloved hand. The Eggplant Man (anthropomorphic eggplant, species: Solanum melongena) turns his head toward her, posture loosening, mouth shifting into a smug half-smile.\n\nSPEAKER BLOCKING:\n- Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman: "آه Mr. Squashalino، باين عليك زوين بزاف." ⚠️ ONLY Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman speaks—Eggplant Man mouth fully closed, he only nods.\n- Eggplant Man: "واخّا؟ شكراً بزاف. خاصنا نمشيو نتعشّاو شي نهار." ⚠️ ONLY Eggplant Man speaks—Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman mouth fully closed, she smiles.\n- Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman: "حتى أنا ما عنديش مانع." ⚠️ ONLY Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman speaks—Eggplant Man mouth fully closed.\n\nTransition: cut to candlelit restaurant date. Emotional arc: seduction succeeds.	Strawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman: "آه Mr. Squashalino، باين عليك زوين بزاف."\nEggplant Man: "واخّا؟ شكراً بزاف. خاصنا نمشيو نتعشّاو شي نهار."\nStrawberry Doctor / Strawberry Woman: "حتى أنا ما عنديش مانع."	Ambience: boutique room tone with distant footsteps and soft chatter. Music: minimalist fashion-house electronic beat at ~100 BPM, cool and sparse. SFX: clothing rack swish, soft glove tap on suit fabric, distant cash register beep. Mix: dialogue forward; music mid-low; ambience subtle.	فمحل Balenciaga، الفراولة كتغازل Mr. Squashalino وكتغذيه بالكلام الزوين، وهو كيرد عليها وكيقترح يخرجو يتعشّاو.	data:image/jpeg;base64,
1	1	1	hook	Strawberry doctor performs cosmetic work on the banana woman while the banana secretly vows to make her ugly	Vertical 9:16. High-end 3D animated cinematic style with smooth glossy fruit surfaces and realistic fabric shading. In a clean cosmetic clinic treatment room, a **Banana Woman (anthropomorphic banana, species: Musaceae)** reclines in a white leather dental-style chair. FULL ANCHOR: tall and slim with athletic legs, bright ripe-yellow peel skin, banana-shaped head with a peeled-back top forming a thick curved peel “hair” draped backward; no eyebrows visible; facial features simplified (eyes not clearly visible in the sampled frame due to motion/blur), nose minimal, mouth small—expression tense; distinguishing marks: none visible. Clothing: fitted sleeveless black ribbed mini dress; no footwear visible; no accessories. Beside her, a **Strawberry Doctor (anthropomorphic strawberry, species: Fragaria)** leans in from frame right wearing a crisp white lab coat over a light shirt, bright-blue nitrile gloves, and a stethoscope partially visible; strawberry head is red with seed speckles and a small green stem; a crown of green leaves with small white flowers sits on top; face details partially obscured in the sample; no visible jewelry. The Strawberry Doctor’s gloved hands touch the Banana Woman’s cheek as if injecting or applying filler. Environment: beige walls with subtle leaf-pattern decor, a white adjustable exam lamp overhead, a metal tray with bottles and tools on the left, pale wood floor. Camera: medium shot, eye-level, slightly angled from the Banana Woman’s left side. Lighting: soft neutral-white clinic lighting from overhead and exam lamp. Palette: beige, white, black, ripe-yellow. Mood: conspiratorial, clinical tension. Key prop: exam lamp positioned above chair; small bottles on tray left.	Duration ~8s. Start with a tight medium shot on the Banana Woman (anthropomorphic banana, species: Musaceae) reclined; camera does a slow 10% push-in. The Strawberry Doctor (anthropomorphic strawberry, species: Fragaria) leans closer, steadies the Banana Woman’s face with the left blue-gloved hand and performs a small precise cosmetic action with the right hand (gentle tapping/injecting motion at the cheek). The Banana Woman’s eyes (not clearly visible) should convey worry and scheming through head tilt and tense shoulders; hands rest on her lap. The Strawberry Doctor’s posture is professional and calm.\n\nSPEAKER BLOCKING:\n- Banana Woman: "غادي نديرها قبيحة، ومن بعد Mr. Squashalino غادي يبغي غير أنا." ⚠️ ONLY Banana Woman speaks this line—Banana Woman mouth moves; Strawberry Doctor mouth fully closed, only hand motions continue.\n\nTransition: quick hard cut to a grimy bathroom mirror scene. Emotional arc: secret malice under clinical calm.	Banana Woman: "غادي نديرها قبيحة، ومن بعد Mr. Squashalino غادي يبغي غير أنا."	Ambience: quiet clinic room tone with faint HVAC hum. Music: low, suspenseful synth pad at ~70 BPM, minimal percussion, mixed under dialogue. SFX: soft latex glove squeaks; tiny metal tool clink on tray; subtle exam lamp mechanical creak; faint liquid/syringe click (if shown). Mix: dialogue front and center; music -18 LUFS under; SFX lightly accent the cheek-touch moment.	فعيادة التجميل، الطبيبة الفراولة كتداوي/كتبدّل فملامح الموزة، والموزة كتتوعد فسرّها أنها غادي تخلّي الفراولة قبيحة باش Mr. Squashalino يبغيها هي.	data:image/jpeg;base64,
